<p>When I thought that SCP-2317 is the best thing that existed on the site&#8230;</p>
<p>I stumbled on this, and my mind is completely blown out of proportion.</p>
<p>This, this gives amend to horrible name that is &quot;Montauk&quot; that's been writhing inside my mind with burning hatred ever since I discovered SCP-231 and permanently scarred by that file. Ever since that day I asked, who's the man who responsible for this absolutely unforgivable inhuman cruelty?</p>
